#: app/templates/help/resource-editor-help.htm:12
msgid ""
"To begin, select a card, enter data, and click <strong>Add</strong>. Some "
"cards may allow multiple instances, in which case you will be able to add as "
"many of the same type as you want."
msgstr ""
"<strong>1. Tautuhitia ngā Paearu Rapunga</strong> - Haere ki te Whārangi "
"rapu, ka tāuru ai i ngā paearu katoa e hiahia ana koe ki te whakamahi hei "
"whirihora i tō Rapunga i Tiakina. Ka kitea pea e koe mā te tāpiritanga o ia "
"tātari rapu hou (ahakoa mā te whakamahi i te tātari kupu, ngā utauta tātari "
"mapi rānei, ngā tātari wā rānei) ka huri te URL mō te whārangi.<br>"
".                              <strong>2. Tāruatia te URL</strong> - I roto "
"i te pae wāhitau o tō pūtirotiro, tāruatia te URL <em>katoa</em>. He aho roa "
"tēnei e tautuhi ana i ngā tātari rapu i hangaia i te hipanga 1.<br>"
".                       <strong>3. Hangaia te rapunga i Tiakina</strong> - "
"Hei mahi whakamutunga, hoki mai ki tēnei whārangi, ka whakakī ai i ngā "
"tautuhinga ka kitea e koe i te taha mauī. Ka taea hoki e koe te tuku atu i "
"tētahi atahanga ka whakakitea i te taha o tō Rapunga i Tiakina."

