#: app/templates/index.htm:216
msgid "Deploy Applications Rapidly"
msgstr "Whakarewa Wawe i ngā Taupānga"

#: app/templates/index.htm:218
msgid ""
"Design custom information management applications in hours.  Build your "
"databases with Arches Designer, then configure your interface all without "
"having to write any code."
msgstr ""
"Hoahoatia ētahi taupānga whakahaere mōhiotanga whakarite i roto i ngā hāora "
"ruarua noa.  Hangaia o pātengi raraunga ki Pūhoahoa Arches, kātahi ka "
"whirihora i tō tāhono, e kore koe e herea kia tuhi waehere."

#: app/templates/index.htm:235
msgid "Interface Manager"
msgstr "Pūwhakahaere Tāhono"

#: app/templates/index.htm:237
msgid ""
"Arches automatically creates data entry forms based on your data models.  "
"Use Arches' Card Manager to configure the look and feel of your data entry "
"UI."
msgstr ""
"Ka hanga aunoa a Arches i ngā puka whakauru raraunga i runga tonu i ō "
"tātauira raraunga.  Whakamahia te Pūwhakahaere Kāri Arches hei whirihora i "
"te āhua me te wairua o tō UI tāuru raraunga."

#: app/templates/index.htm:246
msgid "Data Security"
msgstr "Te Haumaru Raraunga"

#: app/templates/index.htm:248
msgid ""
"Use Arches' Permissions Manager to set up data access rules for all your "
"user groups and individual accounts.  You can define read/write/delete and "
"no-access permissions."
msgstr ""
"Whakamahia te Pūwhakahaere Whakaaetanga Arches hei whakarite i ngā ture "
"urunga raraunga mō ō rōpū kaiwhakamahi me ō pūkete takitahi katoa.  Ka taea "
"e koe te pānui/tuhi/muku me te whakakāhore urunga mō ngā whakaaetanga."

#: app/templates/index.htm:270
msgid "Orchestrate your data entry"
msgstr "Whakaraupapatia tō tāurutanga raraunga"

#: app/templates/index.htm:272
msgid ""
"Design step-wise data management interfaces that simplify complex editing "
"tasks.  Ensure that everyone enters data completely and consistently"
msgstr ""
"Hoahoatia he tāhonotanga whakahaere raraunga ā-hipanga hei whakangāwari i "
"ngā taumahi takatā matatini.   Whakaritea he tikanga e whakauru ai te "
"tangata i te katoa o ngā raraunga, i runga hoki i te āhua ōrite."

#: app/templates/index.htm:295
msgid "Arches Search Tools"
msgstr "Ngā Utauta Rapu Arches"

#: app/templates/index.htm:296
msgid "Find what you're looking for"
msgstr "Kitea tāu e rapu nā"

#: app/templates/index.htm:298
msgid ""
"Arches comes with powerful built-in search tools.  Quickly filter large "
"databases with term, geospatial, and time-based search components"
msgstr ""
"Kei roto i a Arches ōna ake utauta rapu whai kaha.  Kia tere tō tātari i ngā "
"pātengi raraunga rahi mā ōna wae rapu ā-kupu, ā-takiwā matawhenua, ā-wā anō "
"hoki."

#: app/templates/index.htm:311
msgid "Search Options"
msgstr "Ngā Kōwhiringa Rapu"

#: app/templates/index.htm:313
msgid ""
"Arches gives you many ways to find precisely the information you need, even "
"if your Arches application contains 10's of millions of records.  In "
"addition to term, thesaurus, geospatial, and temporal filters, Arches "
"provides you with advanced filtering options that support boolean logic, "
"inverses, and many other filtering options."
msgstr ""
"Ko tā Arches he hoatu ara maha kia kitea pūtia e koe ngā mōhiotanga e hiahia "
"ana koe, ahakoa kei roto i tō taupānga Arches te hia 10 miriona rēkoata.   I "
"tua atu i ngā tātari ā-kupu, ā-papakupu tairite, ā-takiwā matawhenua, ā-wā "
"anō hoki, ka hoatu a Arches i ētahi kōwhiringa tātari hōhonu e tautoko ana i "
"te arorau boolean, ngā kōaro, me ētahi atu whiringa tātari huhua."

#: app/templates/index.htm:317
msgid ""
"Arches' search capabilities also provide for sophisticated data "
"visualizations, including interactive displays of the connections between "
"your data objects using a Force Directed Graph."
msgstr ""
"Ko tā ngā pūmanawa rapu Arches he hora i ētahi whakaahuatanga raraunga "
"matatau, me te whai wāhi o ētahi whakaaturanga pāhekoheko o ngā hononga i "
"waenga i ō ahanoa raraunga mā te whakamahi Kauwhakata Āki Kaha."

#: app/templates/index.htm:321
msgid ""
"If you're a software developer, you can build on Arches modular search "
"services and create your own filters, reports, and visualizations to best "
"show off your particular dataset."
msgstr ""
"Mehemea he kaiwhakawhanake pūmanawa koe, ka taea e koe te hanga mai i ngā "
"ratonga rapu kōwae Arches hei hanga i āu ake tātari, pūrongo,  whakaahua "
"hoki e tino pai ai te whakakite i tō huinga raraunga ake."

